2_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3987, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 201194, "username": "aliensb", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/aliensb", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/63fd/9a75/201194_mini.png?m=1669946009", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/63fd/9a75/201194_normal.png?m=1669946009", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/63fd/9a75/201194_large.png?m=1669946009", "created": 1479092460, "last_modified": 1669946009}, "last_reply_by": "Navee", "last_touched": 1696838188, "title": "孩子明年一月就要出生了，求推荐婴儿车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/980075", "created": 1696811243, "deleted": 0, "content": "由于孩子明年一月就要出生了，最近一直在看婴儿车，各种品牌，各种特点，各种价位，眼睛就开花了。求过来人实际分享下婴儿车实际的挑选着重点，目前看了比较满意的是 Cybex 的 mios3 ，但是感觉有点超出预算了，各位推荐适用的婴儿车。", "content_rendered": "由于孩子明年一月就要出生了，最近一直在看婴儿车，各种品牌，各种特点，各种价位，眼睛就开花了。求过来人实际分享下婴儿车实际的挑选着重点，目前看了比较满意的是 Cybex 的 mios3 ，但是感觉有点超出预算了，各位推荐适用的婴儿车。", "last_modified": 1696811243, "replies": 113, "id": 980075}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1660301119", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1660301119", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 21465, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119", "stars": 5075, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 542637, "username": "Moyyyyyyyyyyye", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Moyyyyyyyyyyye", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac17abf6b7fe02bef9b2e03fee444949?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac17abf6b7fe02bef9b2e03fee444949?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac17abf6b7fe02bef9b2e03fee444949?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1618479560, "last_modified": 1694004920}, "last_reply_by": "elevencd", "last_touched": 1696839001, "title": "[布局重构] Xterminal SSH 布局功能全更新，体验吊打旧版 100 倍😁，顺便继续送 [激活码] ！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/980160", "created": 1696821472, "deleted": 0, "content": "### 更好用的开发工具，但不止于 SSH/Terminal\r\n官网地址： [https://www.xterminal.cn]( https://www.xterminal.cn)\r\n\r\n#### 此次更新几乎重写了 SSH 布局相关的组件，将操作度更高的操作提升到组件级别，并且新增了很多快捷操作按钮\r\n\r\n\r\n🤩🤩🤩另外已经在半个月前支持了自定义背景哦\r\n\r\n![ssh_forward]( https://cdn-cn.xterminal.cn/custom_backgroud.png)\r\n\r\n当然透明背景也不会缺失（颜值永不缺席😍）\r\n\r\n![ssh_forward]( https://cdn-cn.xterminal.cn/opacity.png)\r\n\r\n## 本次更新逻辑图预览，废话不多说\r\n\r\n![ssh_forward]( https://cdn-cn.xterminal.cn/images/MrGcYj6pLofKplWUbqFcaQZoPYxbJncWDS-hu4kdb3E.png)\r\n\r\n![ssh_forward]( https://cdn-cn.xterminal.cn/images/52eLK_033z2BL-zHQiHem4mY7uWsCKW96r5xZt0JbLc.png)\r\n\r\n![ssh_forward]( https://cdn-cn.xterminal.cn/images/r7Gfcg_omnAiDkRb5qAS72oMLfEe3Bqd3v2M3FMkizw.png)\r\n\r\n![ssh_forward]( https://cdn-cn.xterminal.cn/images/em7W0eedF6E4tL-EtT4mQi__3XBL5OXaKBy4X2AxLtA.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n***按照原来的逻辑还是发送激活码，楼层发送，使用了记得 Q 一下，会不定时发送☺️***", "content_rendered": "<h3>更好用的开发工具，但不止于 SSH/Terminal</h3>\n<p>官网地址： <a href=\"https://www.xterminal.cn\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.xterminal.cn</a></p>\n<h4>此次更新几乎重写了 SSH 布局相关的组件，将操作度更高的操作提升到组件级别，并且新增了很多快捷操作按钮</h4>\n<p>🤩🤩🤩另外已经在半个月前支持了自定义背景哦</p>\n<p><img alt=\"ssh_forward\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn-cn.xterminal.cn/custom_backgroud.png\"/></p>\n<p>当然透明背景也不会缺失（颜值永不缺席😍）</p>\n<p><img alt=\"ssh_forward\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn-cn.xterminal.cn/opacity.png\"/></p>\n<h2>本次更新逻辑图预览，废话不多说</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"ssh_forward\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading